To run our application, please make sure you have Google Chrome downloaded.

Steps:
1. Go to the extensions page of Google Chrome (Menu-> More tools-> Extensions)
2. Click on the checkbox labeled "Developer mode" in the top right portion of the page
3. Then click "Load unpacked extension" on the top of the page
4. Direct your file system to the folder labeled "chrome_ext"
5. Click "ok" and our Spoiler Alert extension should exist on your Chrome browser and should be ready for use. 